{"tid":1137262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【五一黃金周】單挑大象篇：西雙版納野象區落車 強國女遭大象踢斷3肋骨","createTime":"2019-05-03T15:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T15:46:57.000Z","uid":103156,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8e21f7bd76493685d9b65570d701027a6b02b515","tid":1137262,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"【五一黃金周】西雙版納野象區落車 強國女遭大象踢斷3肋骨<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190503&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59559583\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190503%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59559583&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW9w5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=9411f9d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190503%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59559583&h=9507fe0c\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190503&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59559583</a><br />\n<br />\n葉女士一行6人從雲南孟連縣駕車到當地，到了野象區後停車，葉女士下車後進入樹林，遭野象襲擊受傷。由上月25日至今，雲南西雙版納已發生多宗野象襲擊人類的事件，導致3人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n事發於昨日早上11時許，葉女士夫婦偕同老人家和孩子到西雙版納野象谷景區遊玩，其間<span style=\"color: red;\">女兒突然感到內急</span>，葉女士的丈夫李先生先下車守在路邊，<span style=\"color: red;\">葉女士便帶孩子進入樹林中如廁，剛巧一頭野象走出樹林</span>，穿越公路走向母女2人。<br />\n<br />\n坐在車上的長輩發現後高呼提醒，李先生急忙衝入樹林抱起女兒，<span style=\"color: red;\">葉女士則跑向公路下的河溪。野象隨即追上，踢了葉女士背脊一腳</span>。<br />\n<br />\n葉女士被送院，證實左腿骨骨折、3根肋骨骨折，無生命危險。"},{"pid":"b550208def34ecad5eef1cfbd7b1bb7848ee8591","tid":1137262,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:24:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xYigma5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxYigma5.png&h=1132be30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1466dc28b0c8c119ab06907cad5f3ab68d125e76","tid":1137262,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:34:23.000Z","msg":"事主被網紅野象「竹筍牙」踢傷，導致左腿及3根肋骨骨折。據悉，竹筍牙在2016年曾襲擊3名維修工人。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K1hT7TX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK1hT7TX.png&h=39269168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據了解，此次已西雙版納州自上月25日起，第4宗野象襲擊人類事件，此前已造成至少3死。專家指出，當地今年少雨乾旱，食物相對不足，野象吃飽後還要去尋找水源，加上處於發情期，會顯得比較爆燥；專家呼籲，市民及遊客在野象活動的區域，應提高警惕，不要貿然下車，在安全區域活動。 (<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190503/mobile/bkn-20190503210547855-0503_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190503%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190503210547855-0503_00952_001.html&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW9w5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=7b2f6a26\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190503/mobile/bkn-20190503210547855-0503_00952_001.html</a>)"},{"pid":"3a2bb0b6f70a3837502341a42279f74e78cbecf1","tid":1137262,"uid":36995,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d8hkNVQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd8hkNVQ.gif&h=b17bfcdd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0abd7def78dd91aafa34e1745844a91fc39ce3dd","tid":1137262,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:39:15.000Z","msg":"渣架"},{"pid":"59d293285db0186b7cf7281b98b37f2ef87aefd3","tid":1137262,"uid":140831,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:40:41.000Z","msg":"聽過象腦係冇「忘記」呢個function<br />\n襲擊人只會因為係以前同人有不愉快經歷"},{"pid":"4c627bbce19a5cc12aa7e7bc9e3b2c6a6d7edc19","tid":1137262,"uid":39698,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:43:39.000Z","msg":"大象果然有靈性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e464f79fee017eb0d0ae1eb8831d04ec3879635c","tid":1137262,"uid":103156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DDjvqKz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDDjvqKz.jpg&h=dcb1d5f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92ca6e7586bad8af5d67c5a6e6edffad1545277f","tid":1137262,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c627bbce19a5cc12aa7e7bc9e3b2c6a6d7edc19","tid":1137262,"uid":39698,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:43:39.000Z","msg":"大象果然有靈性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ifAizDz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FifAizDz.png&h=7b64500c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}